data.description: Well maintained 4 bedroom 2 bath brick home located in booming Newport, KY! Home offers beautiful hardwood floors, spacious rooms, soaring ceilings, and tons of character! Enjoy a morning coffee on the first or second floor porches, or hang out in the flat backyard. The detached garage and large basement offer great storage.
